b2c0009a7098e2","tid":2505293,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"日日新聞唔係個個被清算,就哩個被解散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"eab8c846440097bb1bd9da47ca2cb4074829fa76","tid":2505293,"uid":94771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:03:23.000Z","msg":"係進入政治清算期，公民社會被打壓到已無空間<br />\n<strong><ins>日日都可能有人因為19年抗爭而被靜靜雞清算，比拉返狗屋都無人知</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\"><ins>所以而家好需要的被動報料的哨兵(即見有被捕人士就影)</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong>而家已經講緊會清算<span class=\"maroon\">[b]理大</strong></span>登記手足<br />\n<br />\n可能你影一影，你就救返佢一命<br />\n<br />\n[orange]<strong>日常生活中要做的被動哨兵好重要</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://telegram.groups.hk/cover/8241250102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.groups.hk%2Fcover%2F8241250102.jpg&h=fd287c0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>香港未日期清算好嚴重</ins>，<strong><ins>無聲無色咬人機會大</ins></strong><br />\n<strong>無人報，就真係等主流傳媒出先知，到時都可能係無律師下亂講野了<br />\n<br />\n不論<ins>返工，返學，放學，放工，放飯，出街，買餸</ins><br />\n總知你係條街見到有人被咬走，你去報哨就[b]可能</strong><ins>已經幫到手足</ins>，而你都係一個合格的哨兵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rmQ6bts.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrmQ6bts.jpg&h=2ae33ecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有見到有人被捕影影相唔會好難，可以報去<span class=\"orange\"><strong>＂被捕人士關注組＂</strong></span>，<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/19734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F19734&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B66nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=b36532cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/19734</a><br />\n被捕組 - 拘捕報料 Bot <span class=\"teal\"><strong><ins>(Telegram)</ins></strong></span><br />\n@YOUARENOTALONEHK_BOT<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">需要的係：<ins><strong>時間，地點，相，無相就要特徵</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVguwsh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVguwsh.jpg&h=ff5a31a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外再介紹報哨Channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/The_watcher_channel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FThe_watcher_channel&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B66nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=8617dd84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/The_watcher_channel</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/scottscout\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fscottscout&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B66nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=1b6e0e87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/scottscout</a> （已知暫停運作）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;"}}